A time-travel debugger for SolidJS. This works with our npm package found here: 

https://www.npmjs.com/package/solid-rewind

instructions:
1. install our package with 'npm i solid-rewind'

2. Import our Rewind component at the top level of your application (see screenshot).

3. Wrap your top-level component in our 'Rewind' component (see screenshot).

And That's it! Build your project and open our chrome extension along-side it.
